OL,3,CMan in his late twenties pleads not
OL,4,Cguilty to crimes against five women
OL,6,FA man in his late twenties has pleaded
OL,7,Fnot guilty to ten charges against five
OL,8,Fwomen. They included attempted rape,
OL,9,Fcriminal assault, and threatening
OL,10,Fbehaviour.
OL,12,FAbdelkarim Arfaoui appeared in
OL,13,FJersey's Royal Court for the start of
OL,14,Fhis trial on Monday 13 July.
OL,16,FAll of the incidents took place on the
OL,17,Fmorning of 30th November 2025 during a
OL,18,Fninety minute period.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G1/4
