PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F354A1784054883
OL,3,CMan in his late twenties pleads not
OL,4,Cguilty to crimes against five women
OL,6,FThe Court heard video evidence from
OL,7,Fone victim who said that she thought
OL,8,FArfaoui was going to "kill her", that
OL,9,Fhe was aggressive, grabbing her, and
OL,10,Fstrangling her.
OL,12,FShe said that she was "crying",
OL,13,F"begging him to stop", and was left
OL,14,Ffeeling "ashamed".
OL,16,FThe prosecution detailed the
OL,17,Fexperiences of the other women in
OL,18,Fharrowing detail, including how he
OL,19,Ffollowed them, grabbed them, and
OL,20,Ftouched them.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G2/4
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
