FL,355,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F354A1784054883
OL,3,CMan in his late twenties pleads not
OL,4,Cguilty to crimes against five women
OL,6,FSome of the women were on their way
OL,7,Fhome, going to work, or going to the
OL,8,Fgym.
OL,10,FThe first of the incidents took place
OL,11,Fat the Le Geyt cut-through near
OL,12,FSpringfield Stadium at 6am before
OL,13,Fanother on Clarendon Road at 6:40am,
OL,14,Ffollowed by one ten minutes later, on
OL,15,FOxford Road at 6:50am.
OL,17,FAfter that, Arafoui is alleged to have
OL,18,Fcontinued to Minden Place, where the
OL,19,Fnext attack happened just after 7am.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G3/4
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
