PN,35404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F354A1784054883
OL,3,CMan in his late twenties pleads not
OL,4,Cguilty to crimes against five women
OL,6,FThe last was reported at West Centre
OL,7,Fat 7:21am before the defendant was
OL,8,Farrested on Tunnel Street ten minutes
OL,9,Flater.
OL,11,FThe court also saw CCTV footage of
OL,12,FArafoui following some of the women
OL,13,Fand heard a 999 call placed by one of
OL,14,Fthe alleged victims.
OL,16,FArafoui remains in custody, where he
OL,17,Fwill remain for the duaration of the
OL,18,Ftrial.
OL,20,FIt is expected to last until the end
OL,21,Fof the week.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G4/4
